COMPONENTS REQUIRED

Arduino UNO
Soil moisture sensor with module
5V/12V relay
Water pump 12V, 4A with garden hose connection. Power consumption : max 3.5A Flow rate : max 6 litres per minute
Lead Battery. Voltage : 12V
Power : 10 Ah
Hose 10 mm diameter (2 in quantity)
Sprinkler to connect to hose 10 mm diameter
Electrical connecting wire lines
Jumper wires
